To build this treat modeling tool:

1. Run auto.sh ($ sudo bash auto.sh)
2. You need only one command to run application after completion of all installation packages ($ sudo grunt serve --force)

NOTE:
1. Be assure that all the dependencies and packages are installed correctly
2. You may need manual intervention while runing the script.

You can go through the following links for more details:

https://github.com/mozilla/seasponge

http://mozilla.github.io/seasponge/#/

Sample Example:

Please watch this video:

https://air.mozilla.org/mozilla-winter-of-security-seasponge-a-tool-for-easy-threat-modeling/
